'''Anime Mid-Atlantic''' is a Japanese Animation and cultural festival held in [[Richmond, Virginia]], USA every June. Founded in 2001, Anime Mid-Atlantic's goal is to provide a place where [[anime]] fans can gather together and share in their common interest in a festive and fun atmosphere.
